Overall Progress
Day 102 showed continued improvement with this week’s conversational phrases. The longer travel sentences are becoming much easier to recall, and the weekly challenge phrase is now fully memorized. Pimsleur Lesson 13 introduced several new conversational structures that will require one additional review tomorrow before moving on, but the majority of today’s material was retained well. Compared to Day 100, hesitation continues to decrease, sentence structure is becoming more natural, and more phrases are being recalled automatically instead of translated word-by word 



